creator: National Financial Services
descriptionHtml:
NFS POS app for small business owners that provides POS services and beyond with great capabilities at an affordable rate.
NFS POS helps you directly engage with your customers and gives you a head start on the competition.
The power to thrive while others are failing.
Need to offer curbside or make deliveries?
NOW you can turn delivery into a profit center instead of a loss; you set the price.

No more Credit Card Fees!
The app receives orders from not one consumer app but now has 2 consumer apps (YEStaurants and QIX).
More features for less money.
NFS POS offers what normal POS systems offer plus many more.
Like Curbside, and delivery and many more.
Give it a shot and get an instant free listing.
